title: The Warehouse Phase
overview: Malachi Moore, or Chi for short, is an overlooked musician who begrudgingly dives into the world of content creation and influencers after Nic P, an infamous rapper and influencer, dies unexpectedly. Chi must learn to balance his love for music, his addiction to stardom, and his desperate search for a mysterious record executive all in the unapologetic pursuit of his ultimate goal; fame.
